imdb.plot outline: Voice Of Resistance is the only news program that gives a Judea-Christian and historical perspective, while equipping Viewers to become Political Leaders. Randall Terry has a thirty year history as a Pro-Life Activist, Trainer, Speaker, and Author. He also has a Masters in Foreign Relations and Islamic Studies. With his knowledge of history, his candor when teaching, and his passion to train others, he is on a mission to raise up a new generation to protect Life, Liberty, and Faith.
